OL,3,CCardiff Half Marathon 2025: Historic
OL,4,Cturnout and record-breaking
OL,5,Cperformances
OL,7,FThe 2025 Cardiff Half Marathon saw
OL,8,Frecord-breaking achievements as over
OL,9,F29,000 participants took to the
OL,10,Fstreets of the Welsh capital on
OL,11,FSunday, 5 October.
OL,13,FThe event is the largest edition to
OL,14,Fdate and included more than 4,000
OL,15,Finternational entrants- the highest in
OL,16,Fthe race's 22-year history.
