OL,3,CCardiff Half Marathon 2025: Historic
OL,4,Cturnout and record-breaking
OL,5,Cperformances
OL,7,FDespite windy conditions, runners from
OL,8,Felite athletes to charity fundraisers
OL,9,Fcompleted the scenic route, which
OL,10,Fpassed iconic city landmarks such as
OL,11,FCardiff Castle, the Principality
OL,12,FStadium, and the Wales Millennium
OL,13,FCentre.
OL,15,FEthiopian runner Yismaw Dillu made a
OL,16,Fstandout half marathon debut, setting
OL,17,Fa new course record of 59:22 in the
OL,18,Fmen's race, beating the previous best
OL,19,Ffrom 2019 by over seven seconds.
