OL,3,CCardiff Half Marathon 2025: Historic
OL,4,Cturnout and record-breaking
OL,5,Cperformances
OL,7,FIn the women's event, Miriam Chebet
OL,8,Fsuccessfully defended her title,
OL,9,Ffinishing in 1:06:36- an improvement
OL,10,Fon her winning time from the previous
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FCallum Hall and Mel Nicholls were the
OL,14,Ffirst across the line in the men's and
OL,15,Fwomen's wheelchair races, respectively.
