OL,3,CCardiff Half Marathon 2025: Historic
OL,4,Cturnout and record-breaking
OL,5,Cperformances
OL,7,FThe race embraced the theme 'We're All
OL,8,FIn', highlighting inclusivity and
OL,9,Fshared achievement. More than 500
OL,10,Fvolunteers and numerous cheer
OL,11,Fstations, including the vibrant
OL,12,FPrincipality Rainbow Roundabout, lined
OL,13,Fthe course, contributing to a lively
OL,14,Fatmosphere.
OL,16,FOrganisers have confirmed the event
OL,17,Fwill return on 4 October 2026, with a
OL,18,Fballot system now in place to manage
OL,19,Fgrowing demand.
